@startuml
title BP-00 - End to End School Financial Platform

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Super Admin|
start
:Onboard school tenant;
:Create initial school administrator;

|School Administrator|
:Configure school workspace;
:Assign finance and academic users;

|Academic Staff|
:Maintain students and parent relationships;

|Finance Officer|
:Configure payment policies;
:Configure payment products;
:Generate student obligations;

|Parent Guardian|
:Login and select school workspace;
:View children outstanding bills;
:Select bills to pay;

|Platform|
:Create payment order or invoice;
:Validate payment rules;
:Record payment allocation;
:Update student obligation balance;

if (Payment completed?) then (Yes)
  :Post financial ledger entries;
  :Prepare reporting and audit trail;
else (No)
  :Keep payment order pending or cancelled;
endif

|Finance Officer|
:Review collection, outstanding and ledger reports;
stop

note right
Scope summary:
- Multi tenant school financial platform.
- Student Obligation is the center of billing.
- Payment reduces obligations.
- Ledger records auditable financial evidence.
end note
@enduml
